00:09:34.090 --> 00:09:35.950 align:middle line:10%
as a vestige of the old country.

00:09:35.950 --> 00:09:36.770 align:middle line:10%
They were dirty.

00:09:36.770 --> 00:09:37.570 align:middle line:10%
They were ignorant.

00:09:37.570 --> 00:09:38.690 align:middle line:10%
They were illiterate.

00:09:38.690 --> 00:09:43.420 align:middle line:10%
