00:09:45.160 --> 00:09:46.940 align:middle line:10%
would be cleaner and safer.

00:09:46.940 --> 00:09:49.210 align:middle line:10%
The reality, of course,
was that giving birth

00:09:49.210 --> 00:09:50.832 align:middle line:10%
with an obstetrician
at that time

00:09:50.832 --> 00:09:53.290 align:middle line:10%
was much more dangerous than
giving birth with the midwife,

00:09:53.290 --> 00:09:56.110 align:middle line:10%
because doctors were
graduating from medical school.

00:09:56.110 --> 00:09:58.480 align:middle line:84%
