witnessed a live birth

00:09:58.480 --> 00:10:01.360 align:middle line:90%
before they set out to practice.

00:10:01.360 --> 00:10:05.620 align:middle line:84%
>> What happened was the OB/GYN
specialty hospital started

00:10:05.620 --> 00:10:07.120 align:middle line:90%
to sprout up.

00:10:07.120 --> 00:10:10.750 align:middle line:84%
And those professionals
started to multiply.

00:10:10.750 --> 00:10:12.340 align:middle line:90%
And they needed a job.

00:10:12.340 --> 00:10:13.600 align:middle line:90%
Business took over.

00:10:13.600 --> 00:10:17.050 align:middle line:10%
All of a sudden, the
concept of normal changed.

00:10:17.050 --> 00:10:40.990 align:middle line:90%


00:10:40.990 --> 00:10:43.078 align:middle line:84%
>> Obstetrics-- I said
in the New York Times,

00:10:43.078 --> 00:10:44.620 align:middle line:84%
