2% terror is going to happen.

00:10:52.510 --> 00:10:56.140 align:middle line:84%
And it goes from being
completely normal to 2% terror.

00:10:56.140 --> 00:10:58.000 align:middle line:90%
And when you're in a hospital--

00:10:58.000 --> 00:10:59.830 align:middle line:84%
and I don't like
hospitals, in general.

00:10:59.830 --> 00:11:02.530 align:middle line:84%
The idea that they're not
healing places in general.

00:11:02.530 --> 00:11:05.500 align:middle line:84%
But they are good for
when you have that terror.

