the 90% that have
no complications.

00:11:09.940 --> 00:11:12.640 align:middle line:84%
They come through the hospital
and they're put through these--

00:11:12.640 --> 00:11:15.200 align:middle line:84%
it's like a system where
they're flat on their--

00:11:15.200 --> 00:11:16.000 align:middle line:90%
>> It is, totally.

00:11:16.000 --> 00:11:17.230 align:middle line:90%
>> They want a natural birth.

00:11:17.230 --> 00:11:18.762 align:middle line:84%
They want to have
a vaginal birth.

00:11:18.762 --> 00:11:21.220 align:middle line:84%
And there's all these things
that are stacked against them.

00:11:21.220 --> 00:11:21.535 align:middle line:90%
>> That's right.

00:11:21.535 --> 00:11:21.850 align:middle line:90%
Absolutely.

00:11:21.850 --> 00:11:23.398 align:middle line:84%
>> They've told
women, come to us.

00:11:23.398 --> 00:11:24.940 align:middle line:10%
