00:12:36.050 --> 00:12:38.960 align:middle line:84%
Oh, it's been 12 hours,
so now you need Pitocin.

00:12:38.960 --> 00:12:43.460 align:middle line:84%
>> I did know the pressure was
on as we got into 20 hours,

00:12:43.460 --> 00:12:44.690 align:middle line:90%
21 hours.

00:12:44.690 --> 00:12:46.400 align:middle line:84%
>> At the hospital,
I had Pitocin.

00:12:46.400 --> 00:12:49.700 align:middle line:84%
And then that made me itchy,
so they give you something else

00:12:49.700 --> 00:12:50.660 align:middle line:90%
for your itching.

00:12:50.660 --> 00:12:52.820 align:middle line:84%
>> I knew once they
gave you that Pitocin,

00:12:52.820 --> 00:12:53.870 align:middle line:90%
you need the epidural.

00:12:53.870 --> 00:12:55.460 align:middle line:84%
>> You feel better now
that you have the epidural?

00:12:55.460 --> 00:12:56.300 align:middle line:90%
>> Oh my God, yes.

00:12:56.300 --> 00:12:58.580 align:middle line:84%
>> And then things
come on really strong,

00:12:58.580 --> 00:12:59.880 align:middle line:90%
so then you get an epidural.

00:12:59.880 --> 00:13:02.380 align:middle line:84%
>> And if you're uncomfortable,
we can always give you more.

00:13:02.380 --> 00:13:04.797 align:middle line:84%
>> It was very easy for them
to start doing things that we

00:13:04.797 --> 00:13:07.455 align:middle line:84%
hadn't really wanted them to
do, like Pitocin and whatnot,

00:13:07.455 --> 00:13:09.080 align:middle line:84%
because I already
had the IV in my arm.

00:13:09.080 --> 00:13:11.240 align:middle line:84%
>> They don't really
give you the option.

00:13:11.240 --> 00:13:14.062 align:middle line:84%
>> And then another epidural,
because nothing was happening.

00:13:14.062 --> 00:13:15.770 align:middle line:84%
>> You're having a
contraction right now.

00:13:15.770 --> 00:13:16.822 align:middle line:90%
>> I don't feel the pain.

00:13:16.822 --> 00:13:19.280 align:middle line:84%
>> Automatically, they were
like, oh, you need an epidural.

00:13:19.280 --> 00:13:20.605 align:middle line:90%
We'll get the anesthesiologist.

00:13:20.605 --> 00:13:21.980 align:middle line:84%
>> So she's getting
her epidural,

00:13:21.980 --> 00:13:23.938 align:middle line:84%
then we'll put in the
