00:13:23.938 --> 00:13:26.720 align:middle line:84%
>> They gave me another
drug called Stadol.

00:13:26.720 --> 00:13:28.250 align:middle line:90%
>> 17 hours of Pitocin.

00:13:28.250 --> 00:13:31.490 align:middle line:84%
>> They gave me that and
