00:13:31.490 --> 00:13:32.720 align:middle line:90%
I was like, what's going on?

00:13:32.720 --> 00:13:33.080 align:middle line:90%
What's going on?

00:13:33.080 --> 00:13:34.080 align:middle line:90%
There's something wrong.

00:13:34.080 --> 00:13:35.390 align:middle line:90%
>> Cervidil was the end.

00:13:35.390 --> 00:13:38.660 align:middle line:84%
Once Cervidil happened, any
chance beyond that was gone.

00:13:38.660 --> 00:13:39.530 align:middle line:90%
It was gone.

00:13:39.530 --> 00:13:40.970 align:middle line:90%
>> I hated that drug.

00:13:40.970 --> 00:13:44.750 align:middle line:84%
>> It seemed to me that once
they started an intervention,

00:13:44.750 --> 00:13:46.100 align:middle line:90%
they all just--

00:13:46.100 --> 00:13:47.343 align:middle line:90%
it was a domino effect.

00:13:47.343 --> 00:13:49.385 align:middle line:84%
>> The whole thing is like
a big snowball effect.

00:13:49.385 --> 00:13:52.840 align:middle line:90%


00:13:52.840 --> 00:13:55.520 align:middle line:84%
>> In the hospital, you're
not allowed to have very long

00:13:55.520 --> 00:13:56.320 align:middle line:90%
labors.

00:13:56.320 --> 00:13:59.000 align:middle line:84%
So if you are not
dilating rapidly,

00:13:59.000 --> 00:14:00.520 align:middle line:84%
which you're likely
not to do if you

00:14:00.520 --> 00:14:04.000 align:middle line:84%
get an epidural early in labor,
you will be given Pitocin.

00:14:04.000 --> 00:14:05.590 align:middle line:84%
They'll put the
