00:16:00.430 --> 00:16:03.730 align:middle line:84%
because putting the mother flat
on her back literally makes

00:16:03.730 --> 00:16:04.630 align:middle line:90%
the pelvis smaller.

00:16:04.630 --> 00:16:06.850 align:middle line:84%
It makes it much more
difficult for the woman

00:16:06.850 --> 00:16:09.790 align:middle line:84%
to use her stomach muscles
to push, and therefore

00:16:09.790 --> 00:16:12.970 align:middle line:84%
makes it much more likely
that an episiotomy will be cut

00:16:12.970 --> 00:16:16.220 align:middle line:84%
or forceps will be used or the
vacuum extractor will be used.

00:16:16.220 --> 00:16:23.140 align:middle line:10%
[NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]

00:16:23.140 --> 00:16:25.390 align:middle line:10%
>> When the baby
goes in the womb,

00:16:25.390 --> 00:16:29.650 align:middle line:10%
she starts the birth like
