00:16:40.070 --> 00:16:42.380 align:middle line:84%
And that means that
the baby's moving,

00:16:42.380 --> 00:16:43.990 align:middle line:84%
and then he goes
a little bit more.

00:16:43.990 --> 00:16:45.760 align:middle line:84%
And then he needs
to do it again.

00:16:45.760 --> 00:17:11.130 align:middle line:10%
[NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]

00:17:11.130 --> 00:17:14.525 align:middle line:90%
>> Push, push.

00:17:14.525 --> 00:17:16.829 align:middle line:10%
>> Push, push, push.

00:17:16.829 --> 00:17:22.740 align:middle line:10%
[NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]

00:17:22.740 --> 00:17:26.130 align:middle line:84%
>> Women have given up
their autonomy about birth.

00:17:26.130 --> 00:17:29.160 align:middle line:10%
Women are so afraid of
birth, because you do not

00:17:29.160 --> 00:17:32.530 align:middle line:10%
