00:17:32.530 --> 00:17:35.400 align:middle line:84%
Women in America don't know
what's normal about birth.

00:17:35.400 --> 00:17:38.550 align:middle line:84%
>> They watch A Baby Story
and they watch Maternity Ward.

00:17:38.550 --> 00:17:40.080 align:middle line:90%
They watch these programs.

00:17:40.080 --> 00:17:42.990 align:middle line:84%
I think there's a
lot of fear instilled

00:17:42.990 --> 00:17:44.280 align:middle line:90%
in women around birth.

00:17:44.280 --> 00:17:48.380 align:middle line:90%


00:17:48.380 --> 00:17:51.740 align:middle line:10%
>> Every birth that you see on
television is women screaming

00:17:51.740 --> 00:17:54.320 align:middle line:10%
