00:19:08.750 --> 00:19:11.270 align:middle line:84%
It's not as if I'm just going
to pull the baby out of you.

00:19:11.270 --> 00:19:14.500 align:middle line:84%
I'm just going to
assist in your effort.

00:19:14.500 --> 00:19:15.550 align:middle line:90%
Because it's time.

00:19:15.550 --> 00:19:19.600 align:middle line:84%
>> You get a one-sided story
