00:19:24.430 --> 00:19:26.060 align:middle line:90%
>> What is the risk to the baby?

00:19:26.060 --> 00:19:26.860 align:middle line:90%
>> Minimal.

00:19:26.860 --> 00:19:29.650 align:middle line:84%
>> So if you're in labor
