era, when there were communes.

00:34:24.330 --> 00:34:28.030 align:middle line:10%
And the communes mimicked
in many ways immigration

00:34:28.030 --> 00:34:28.830 align:middle line:10%
communities.

00:34:28.830 --> 00:34:31.350 align:middle line:90%
They mimicked extended families.

00:34:31.350 --> 00:34:35.280 align:middle line:84%
And so midwives were reborn,
