00:34:35.280 --> 00:34:37.409 align:middle line:90%
>> We wanted the choices.

00:34:37.409 --> 00:34:39.900 align:middle line:10%
We didn't want somebody
else making the rules that

00:34:39.900 --> 00:34:41.460 align:middle line:10%
didn't understand
us-- that thought

00:34:41.460 --> 00:34:45.150 align:middle line:10%
