00:34:45.150 --> 00:34:48.090 align:middle line:84%
Because we knew that
feelings affected birth.

00:34:48.090 --> 00:34:56.690 align:middle line:90%


00:34:56.690 --> 00:34:59.510 align:middle line:84%
>> That was part of what sparked
the natural childbirth movement

00:34:59.510 --> 00:35:02.990 align:middle line:84%
