abuses of the scopolamine era,

00:35:02.990 --> 00:35:03.965 align:middle line:90%
the twilight sleep era.

00:35:03.965 --> 00:35:06.590 align:middle line:84%
Because some people realized the
only way to get away from that

00:35:06.590 --> 00:35:08.510 align:middle line:84%
was to get out of the
hospital altogether.

00:35:08.510 --> 00:35:11.930 align:middle line:90%


00:35:11.930 --> 00:35:13.790 align:middle line:84%
Just as we were
getting someplace,

00:35:13.790 --> 00:35:16.040 align:middle line:84%
