01:05:52.920 --> 01:05:56.160 align:middle line:84%
And the oxytocin travels in the
bloodstream down to the uterus

01:05:56.160 --> 01:06:00.660 align:middle line:84%
to start triggering the
contractions of labor.

01:06:00.660 --> 01:06:03.540 align:middle line:84%
And that's when the switch to
the maternal brain circuits.

01:06:03.540 --> 01:06:05.580 align:middle line:90%
The mommy brain gets flipped on.

01:06:05.580 --> 01:06:09.960 align:middle line:84%
And the whole brain cocktail
of hormones and neurochemicals

01:06:09.960 --> 01:06:12.330 align:middle line:84%
has, for millions of
years, been developed

01:06:12.330 --> 01:06:16.200 align:middle line:84%
to keep the mommy absolutely
riveted on protection

01:06:16.200 --> 01:06:17.265 align:middle line:90%
of the helpless infant.

01:06:17.265 --> 01:06:23.970 align:middle line:90%


01:06:23.970 --> 01:06:25.770 align:middle line:84%
