01:06:35.040 --> 01:06:36.220 align:middle line:90%
would in the brain.

01:06:36.220 --> 01:06:37.830 align:middle line:84%
So there's all kinds
of things about

01:06:37.830 --> 01:06:39.270 align:middle line:90%
modern medical interventions.

01:06:39.270 --> 01:06:41.580 align:middle line:84%
Sometimes they need to
be done, but they also

01:06:41.580 --> 01:06:45.870 align:middle line:84%
inhibit this natural maternal
aggression to protect the baby

01:06:45.870 --> 01:06:48.730 align:middle line:84%
and to nourish the
baby right after birth

01:06:48.730 --> 01:06:52.005 align:middle line:84%
