take care of her baby.

01:08:27.740 --> 01:08:28.750 align:middle line:10%
It's simple.

01:08:28.750 --> 01:08:32.920 align:middle line:10%
If monkeys give birth
by cesarean section,

01:08:32.920 --> 01:08:35.710 align:middle line:10%
